    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你在 Anomalum 中醒来，陷入了无尽的噩梦。仔细观察你的周围环境，并检查时钟以逃脱。在这款心理恐怖游戏中，注意细节和探索边缘空间对于从噩梦中解脱至关重要。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050480/extras/f05611a22f79173617ed2222bf9483db.poster.avif?t=1761183105\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050480/extras/f05611a22f79173617ed2222bf9483db.webm?t=1761183105\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050480/extras/f05611a22f79173617ed2222bf9483db.mp4?t=1761183105\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>规则</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 不要忽略任何异常。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果你发现异常，立即后退。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果没有异常，继续前进。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >时钟上的时间将指示你是否在进展。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050480/extras/5257b68d9f40f7c81660ef35c0ff0ab6.poster.avif?t=1761183105\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050480/extras/5257b68d9f40f7c81660ef35c0ff0ab6.webm?t=1761183105\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050480/extras/5257b68d9f40f7c81660ef35c0ff0ab6.mp4?t=1761183105\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>特点</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >受 TheExit8 启发的冒险和探索，拥有新的地方等待发现。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >具有挑战性的谜题需要分析环境以寻找异常。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沉浸式的氛围，伴随环绕声和详细的图形，将你完全带入游戏中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏时间</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >20~30分钟</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Anomalum 挑战你利用你的感知来找到出口。你能逃脱吗？</p>",
